nodes.bodyText:
Add tests with precisions up to 12. You'll need to move these to BaseTestTimestamp to take advantage of the new assertj-based assertions. E.g.,
assertThat(assertions.expression("TIMESTAMP '2020-05-01 12:34:56.123456789012'"))
        .hasType(createTimestampType(12))
        .isEqualTo(timestamp(12, 2020, 5, 1, 12, 34, 56, 123_456_789_012L));

I added more tests in BaseTestTimestamp. I kept the tests here, however.
Also, please add/port any relevant tests to #3947
